HEADWORD: Dhow
<hw>Dhow</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ar.
<ets>d⟦amac⟧o</ets>?]</ety> <def>A coasting vessel of Arabia, East
Africa, and the Indian Ocean. It has generally but one mast and a lateen
sail.</def> <altsp>[Also written <asp>dow</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

